## Deployment

### Domain & Hosting
- [ ] Purchase domain (mohamedazab.dev) from Namecheap or Cloudflare
- [ ] Deploy to Vercel (import from GitHub)
- [ ] Add Supabase environment variables to Vercel
- [ ] Connect custom domain in Vercel settings
- [ ] Configure DNS records (A record + CNAME for www) mohamedazab.dev
- [ ] Verify SSL certificate

### Post-Deployment
- [ ] Test live site thoroughly
- [ ] Run Lighthouse audit (aim for 90+ scores)
- [ ] Submit sitemap to Google Search Console
- [ ] Set up monitoring/uptime checks
- [ ] Share portfolio link!!!!! 

